        <h2>
            音调未定的传统的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5928368">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5928368/" class="title-link">新版与旧版</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5928368"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/43326844/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u43326844-12.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/43326844/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">竹雨清风</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-05-05"
      class="main-meta">2013-05-05 23:54:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5928368_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  看过旧版的《音调未定的传统》，发现这版增加了部分内容，而且在内容安排上可能也比之前的内容更加细致一些，内容会更新一些吧。毕竟原来的版本很老了。不过，仍然是一部值得一阅的书，这样对于中国嘉庆以来至民国初年的那段历史会更熟悉一些、更深刻一些。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5928368_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5928368_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










